You must have the following packages installed:

    python-crypto
    python-paramiko
    python-netaddr

    RHEL 5 may require python-simplejson
   
For testing, you will need the following additional packages:

    python-nose

To run directly from source:

    PYTHONPATH=~/src/rho/src bin/rho

To run all tests, install the python-nose package and from the root of the 
project:

    nosetests
